headline: Coinbase Earnings Loom: Is Coin Stock A Buy Now As It Holds Key Level?
summary: Coinbase is holding the 50-day moving average with earnings due on Thursday.  Is Coinbase stock a buy now?  Shares bounced 17% on April 9 when President Donald Trump announced a 90-day pause on tariffs for most countries.

headline: NewLimit, founded by Coinbase CEO Brian Armstrong, raises $130M to develop age-reversing treatments
summary: NewLimit, a startup that aims to increase how long people can live a healthy life by genetically programming their cells, has raised a $130 million Series B led by Kleiner Perkins. New investors Nat Friedman, Daniel Gross, and Khosla Ventures also invested, as did returning backers Founders Fund, Dimension Capital, Elad Gil, Garry Tan, Patrick Collison, and others. The fundraise comes two years after the company raised a $40 million Series A. Founded over four years ago by Coinbase CEO Brian Arm
